                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 21558/8.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Straus</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Pera</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-10-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 30, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Straus states that the Sublime Porte says it has requested the Khedive to
                    prosecute Rizk. Adds that the American Consulate at Cairo has been advised.</p>
            </div>
